<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/treasury-solicitor-s-department> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Treasury Solicitor’s Department (TSol) was a non-ministerial government department that provided legal services to the majority of central government departments and often represented government departments and other publicly funded bodies in England and Wales. On 1 April 2015 TSol became the Government Legal Department (GLD)."@en .
